<l>pukaḻpurin tillilōrk killai yikaḻvārmuṉ</l>
<l>ṉēṟupōṟ pīṭu naṭai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The man who lacks a wife who yearns for praise, lacks before his scorners</l>
<l>a lion-like stately step.</l>
